# Glyphion Project Structure

This Flutter project follows a clean architecture with specific conventions:

1. Entry point is [lib/main.dart](mdc:lib/main.dart)
2. Follow the directory structure:
   - models/ - Data models
   - screens/ - UI screens
   - widgets/ - Reusable components
   - utils/ - Helper functions
   - services/ - Business logic

3. Use setState for state management (no complex state management libraries)
4. Use shared_preferences for data persistence